3 new capabilities, all backwards-compatible:

1. Demo packets (lib/demo-packets/, components/landing/DemoPacketBar.tsx)
   - 3 prefilled real Indian medtechs: CerviAI, EkaScribe, Forus 3nethra
   - Click-to-prefill on /start: fills name/email/mobile/one-liner/url +
     stores wizard answers server-side so synthesis lands in <30 seconds
   - URL pattern: /start?demo=cerviai
   - Tagged in DB via meta.is_demo + new is_demo column
   - Real wizard enum values verified against lib/wizard/types.ts

2. Regulation count chip (components/card/RegulationCountBadge.tsx)
   - Honest count of how many of 9 regulations apply
   - No composite score (different reg burdens are not commensurable)
   - Hover reveals breakdown: required / conditional / N/A
   - Wired into BadgeRow (additional badge, not replacement)

3. Supabase migration (supabase/migration-feature-8-trl-fields.sql)
   - Additive: trl_level, trl_track, trl_completion_pct, is_demo cols
   - All nullable / defaulted, no breaking changes
   - Idempotent backfill from readiness_card JSONB
   - Index on trl_level (partial, where not null)
   - Sync wired into run-synthesis save path

Demo flow: /start → click 'Vyuhaa CerviAI →' → fields prefilled → click
Continue → submit → wizard skipped (answers prefilled server-side) →
synthesis → readiness card with TRL block + reg count.

Verified: typecheck clean, lint clean (3 pre-existing warnings only).
